<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 18 (Xinhua) -- Vice-Premier Jiang Chunyun
today urged local officials not to have a trust-your-luck attitude
toward flood control this year, and to be prepared to protect big
rivers and reservoirs in the upcoming flood season.
</P>
<P>
Jiang, also head of the State Flood Control and Drought-Relief
