in charge of anti-flood issues, who are here to attend a national
conference.
</P>
<P>
Despite the fact that systematic flood control projects along
major rivers have taken shape and that the people have become more
experienced in controlling floods, there are still many potential
risks, he noted.
</P>
<P>
With the flood season coming in about three months, there is
difficult and pressing work to be done, he said.  
</P>
