<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, February 18 (Xinhua) -- Two groups totaling 198
Vietnamese migrants (VMs) returned today by air to Hanoi, Vietnam,
on the 95th and 96th flights under the Orderly Repatriation
Program (ORP), Hong Kong government sources said.
</P>
