<HEADLINE> Sri Lanka's Military Resumes offensive in North </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, February 18 (Xinhua) -- Sri Lankan government troops
Monday resumed its code-named operation "Edi Bala' (Fearless
Force) in the North into the Tamil rebel territory after a 10-day
break, military sources said today.
</P>
