defense lines consolidated after 4-day operation which commenced
on February 5, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
The troops are expected to continue more forcefully into the
rebel territory in the next few days.
</P>
<P>
The Tamil rebels have been fighting a guerrilla war against the
government for a separate state in the north-east of the island
country since 1983.  
