Guard Derek Harper and rookie centre Samaki Walker are the only
players in training camp in October who are still with the Mavs.
</P>
<P>
The trade was announced less than an hour after New Jersey's
108-101 loss at Cleveland and one hour before Dallas's game at
Vancouver. The NBA trading deadline is Thursday evening.  
