</P>
<P>
But in a clear signal to the West, Primakov reiterated earlier
in Moscow his strong opposition to an enlargement of the Western
military alliance.
</P>
<P>
"I'm not an anti-Western person, but an alliance (with the
West) at whatever price would not be acceptable to me," Primakov
said. 
